AND TEXT YOUR WIFE ABOUT IT?

28:31.040 --> 28:33.042
GET OUT OF MY OFFICE,
BENFORD.

28:33.042 --> 28:35.915
I DON'T WANNA SEE
YOUR FACE RIGHT NOW.

28:39.989 --> 28:43.192
KONNICHIWA.
OGENKI DESU KA?

28:43.192 --> 28:45.855
GENKU DESU. ANATA WA?

28:45.855 --> 28:48.998
