39:54.823 --> 39:55.964
NO, YOU...

39:58.597 --> 40:00.469
YOU DON'T GET IT.

40:00.469 --> 40:02.601
SHE'S BROKEN,

40:02.601 --> 40:04.433
ANGRY, SCARED.

40:04.433 --> 40:07.075
SHE DRINKS HERSELF TO SLEEP
EVERY NIGHT.

40:07.075 --> 40:09.978
SHE'S A MESSED UP ALCOHOLIC,
MARK.

40:09.978 --> 40:13.982
AND I'M TO BLAME...
FOR ALL OF IT.

40:13.982 --> 40:17.716
SHE ENLISTED BECAUSE SHE
WANTED TO BE JUST LIKE ME.

40:19.888 --> 40:27.025
AND NOW SHE DRINKS
JUST LIKE ME.

40:27.025 --> 40:29.928
THERE'S NOT A DAMN THING
THAT I CAN DO ABOUT IT.

40:37.766 --> 40:38.937
(sniffles)

40:41.510 --> 40:44.813
LOOK, WE'VE CROSSED
A LINE HERE...

40:44.813 --> 40:47.846
FOR BETTER OR WORSE.

40:47.846 --> 40:51.980
SO, UH...

40:51.980 --> 40:54.983
I DON'T THINK I CAN BE
YOUR SPONSOR ANYMORE, MARK.

40:54.983 --> 40:57.556
I'M SORRY.

40:57.556 --> 41:00.158
(voice breaking) BUT I COULD
REALLY USE A FRIEND.

41:04.733 --> 41:08.036
YOU GOT IT.

41:08.036 --> 41:11.069
(roaring)

41:11.069 --> 41:14.703
